import {useParams } from "react-router-dom"; import React from "react"; import "./DoctorDetails.css"; import axios from "axios"; const baseURL = "http://localhost:7000/doctorData/"; export default function App() { const [previous, setNew] = React.useState([{}]); React.useEffect(() => { axios.get(baseURL).then((response) => { setNew(response.data); }); }, []); const { id } = useParams(); const data = previous.find((x) => x._id === (id)); if (!data) return null; return (

{data.awards}

{data.name}

{data.specialization}


{data.experience} experience


Fee: {data.fee}


{data.clinic_location}


Description of Doctor

{data.description}

{data.name}

{data.email}

{data.phoneNO}

); }
